issue.title: Elo updates displayed only to person who pressed record
issue.body: Make updates through firestore, not through the DOM. While we're at it, display it with difference from previous elo with a green/red arrow for up/down movement.

issue.title: Double counting of games
issue.body: Multiple people can click on "record", making the game count more than once. Fix with making the record popup not get triggered through the database but only from the DOM, so it's local to the device where the winning goal was recorded.
